metadata.name: SYRIA EDITION
metadata.description:
I wanted to make an Open Edition and donate all the proceeds to a charity helping those in South-Central Turkey, Jordan, Syria, Lebanon - who were struck by a 7.8 magnitude earthquake. Death toll rises to 1,639 while 6,000+ injured & is continuing to rise. 

I will be donating to the two following charities (50/50 split) - You are free to donate without minting the NFT: 

International Rescue Committee - https://thegivingblock.com/donate/international-rescue-committee/ 

Medici Senza Frontiere Onlus - https://thegivingblock.com/donate/medici-senza-frontiere-onlus/
